cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper discusses the optimization of deep neural networks, which is a core topic in machine learning. The paper specifically focuses on distributed training, which involves parallelizing the optimization process across multiple machines. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.CV (Computer Vision), as the paper discusses object classification and detection in automatic driver assistance systems. The paper also touches on topics related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
